OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA mainly dry, bright morning.
OL,6,FTurning overcast through the afternoon
OL,7,Fas a band of occasionally heavy rain
OL,8,Fspreads in from the west. Freshening
OL,9,Fafternoon winds, occasionally strong
OL,10,Fin the west.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA cloudy, wet evening with
OL,13,Foccasionally heavy rain spreading
OL,14,Feastwards. Turning drier through the
OL,15,Frest of the night with some clearer
OL,16,Fspells developing. Blustery winds,
OL,17,Fstrong at times.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
