OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FA bright, breezy and largely
OL,6,Fdry day, with sunny spells and just
OL,7,Fthe slight chance of an isolated light
OL,8,Fshower in the west.
OL,9,
OL,10,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FA
OL,11,Fchangeable, often cloudy and breezy
OL,12,Ffew days with spells of rain, but some
OL,13,Fdrier and brighter periods too.
